@startuml
actor "Alice (Expéditeur)" as UserA
participant "Client A (MLS)" as ClientA
participant "Chat Gateway (DS)" as Gateway
participant "Redis (Pub/Sub)" as Redis
participant "Kafka (Topic: chat-messages)" as Kafka
participant "Client B (MLS)" as ClientB
participant "Chat History Service" as History
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

UserA -> ClientA: Tape "Bonjour"

note right of ClientA
  MLS Application Message
  1. Récupération État Groupe
  2. Protect(plain_text) -> MLS Ciphertext
end note

ClientA -> Gateway: WebSocket Send {type: "mls_message", payload: "..."}

note right of Gateway: Gateway agit comme\nDelivery Service (DS)

Gateway -> Gateway: Validate Payload Size/Type

par Distribution Temps Réel (Fan-out)
    Gateway -> Redis: PUBLISH "chat_events" (MLS Blob)
    Redis -> Gateway: OnMessage (Gateway Instance B)
    Gateway -> ClientB: WebSocket Message {type: "mls_message", payload: "..."}
else Persistance Asynchrone
    Gateway -> Kafka: Produce Record
    Kafka --> History: Consommation Event
    History -> MongoDB: Sauvegarde Blob MLS (Opaque)
end

ClientB -> ClientB: MLS Process(Ciphertext)
note right of ClientB
  Déchiffrement & 
  Mise à jour État Groupe (Ratchet)
end note

ClientB --> UserA: (Optionnel) Delivery Receipt
@enduml
